  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a fondue pot over medium heat.",
    "Add cinnamon and ginger powders and sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add Saskatoon berries and cook for 2-3 minutes until they start to caramelize.",
    "Add rice pilaf mix and stir to combine.",
    "Add honey and lemon juice, and mix well.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer for 5-7 minutes until the liquid is absorbed.",
    "Stir in chopped walnuts and serve hot.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with additional Saskatoon berries if desired."
